collector.data
Interface Element

All Known Implementing Classes:
CellInt, CellStr, Enregistrement, Field, Header, Table
public interface Element

An Element is the basic piece of data. It can be saved/read as xml, displayed as a String. It has a type, a data and a label. It can also have a parent.
